Title: Samba Shoes | adidas US
Content: Price $ 80 . Samba OG Shoes Kids.What are adidas Sambas shoes for? The adidas Samba is a soccer shoe first introduced in 1950, designed for training, futsal and street soccer. Its gum rubber outsole with pivot points offers great traction for nimble movements.
